lass=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Archdemons and Side Rituals</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the mighty Archdemons in Main Rituals to advance Letifer's story and open up new Biomes.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or test your mettle (and gather some resources!) in quirky Side Rituals!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294640/extras/1485c6d3e44d8e94fdae9edb6035180f.poster.avif?t=1769159139\" width=800 height=590 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294640/extras/1485c6d3e44d8e94fdae9edb6035180f.webm?t=1769159139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294640/extras/1485c6d3e44d8e94fdae9edb6035180f.mp4?t=1769159139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Motley Crew</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you're not running rituals, chat up your friends in the Hub: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Amabel – A skillful mechanic with a cheerful personality. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Orson – Brains of the operation, with a flair of dark magic. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lucien –  A mysterious, deep-pocketed vampire keeping the operation afloat.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn their story and gain useful tips!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294640/extras/5d05a6fc232440f7dd1c800ea08f2b1c.avif?t=1769159139\" width=595 height=240 /></span></p>",
